snippet: Jordan Spieth had a post-Masters letdown, shooting a three-over-par 74 at the RBC Heritage in Hilton Head Island, S.C., to end his run of 16 straight rounds under par.
abstract: Jordan Spieth finishes RBC Heritage with three-over-par 74, breaking his streak of 16 rounds under par; other golf scores noted.
